title: Automatic T-shirt bag cutting equipment US-XYQ-600

title_en: Automatic T-shirt bag cutting equipment US-XYQ-600
short_description: This US-XYQ-600 model machine cuts t-shirt-shaped handle packages from roll films. The production capacity of the equipment is 60-160 pieces/min*4, the total power is 7 kW, the weight is 1300 kg, and the size is 5.3 * 1.2 * 1.8 m. There are other models of this equipment in the description, and their prices differ from each other.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-XYQ-600 modeldagi uskuna rulonli plyonkalardan mayka shaklidagi tutqichli paketlarni kesib beradi. Uskunaning ishlab chiqarish quvvati 60-160 dona/min*4, umumiy quvvati 7 kW, vazni 1300 kg va o'lchami 5.3 * 1.2 * 1.8 m ni tashkil qiladi. Tavsifda ushbu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham mavjud va ularning narxlari bir-biridan farqlanadi.

long_description:
This US-XYQ-600 model machine cuts t-shirt-shaped handle packages from roll films. The production capacity of the equipment is 60-160 pieces/min*4, the total power is 7 kW, the weight is 1300 kg, and the size is 5.3 * 1.2 * 1.8 m. There are other models of this equipment in the description, and their prices differ from each other.
